lines.text:
[To John Eastland]
You want to clean out the streets? *I am* the streets!
Look at this shit man! 13 dollars and some change, this fucking broad!
This watch ain't nothin' to brag about, it's phoney cartier!
Did you see the look on her face when I put it through her?
I like it when their faces go crazy like that, when they think the world has gone psycho and there's no way out.
[The Exterminator shows up and torches them both]
